-context/`, created by `setup.sh`\")\n\n---\n**Authored-By**: `Claude Code Agent`\n**Model**: `Claude Opus 4.6`","files":null},{"type":4,"timestamp":1772224975,"nonce":"9FnxH+GI+gqVTkKJlsvbEVGvc18=","metadata":{"github-id":"CE_lADOQ241x87uTZbYzwAAAAVjo-ni"},"status":2}]}